            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/351.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Heat</strong> a large, dry, wide based pan (preferably non stick) on a high heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>When</strong> hot, add the lamb koftas</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cook</strong> for 5 min, turning them regularly so they cook evenly</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> charred on all sides, transfer them to a baking tray (use foil to avoid mess)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Place</strong> in the oven for 8-10 min until they are firm to touch&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
